trans-unit.source: Allows a custom override of the <see cref="M:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.DependencyObject.GetValue(System.Workflow.ComponentModel.DependencyProperty)" /> logic associated with a dependency property that is defined on a dependency object.
trans-unit.target: 允許與在相依性物件上定義的相依性屬性相關聯之 <see cref="M:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.DependencyObject.GetValue(System.Workflow.ComponentModel.DependencyProperty)" /> 邏輯的自訂覆寫。

trans-unit.source: An <see cref="T:System.Object" /> that represents the value of the designated <see cref="T:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.DependencyProperty" />.
trans-unit.target: <see cref="T:System.Object" />，其表示所指定 <see cref="T:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.DependencyProperty" /> 的值。

trans-unit.source: The implemetation of this delegate can be set on the <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.PropertyMetadata.GetValueOverride%2A> property of <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.PropertyMetadata> while calling <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.DependencyProperty.Register%2A> or <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.DependencyProperty.RegisterAttached%2A>.
trans-unit.target: 這個委派的實作可在 <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.PropertyMetadata.GetValueOverride%2A> 的 <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.PropertyMetadata> 屬性上設定，同時呼叫 <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.DependencyProperty.Register%2A> 或 <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.DependencyProperty.RegisterAttached%2A>。
